Steps to run this project:
1. Clone this project
2. run 'npm install' command
3. run 'npm start -- --reset-cache' first you need to run this command after that you can use 'npx react-native run-android' or 'npx react-native start'
You are all set to run this project


Suggestion:
1. used reanimated version "3.4.1" //there were few issues in the reanimated version "3.4.0" like 
   "Error while updating property 'transform' of a view managed by: RCTView, js engine: reanimated"
    i.e reanimated version "3.4.1" is recommended specially for the windows users.
